{"tid":2148658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"部長議員紛請辭 或提前選舉解危機","createTime":"2020-08-10T04:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:45:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3abf5037050acb22dfe5556a4d131341b80042","tid":2148658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200810/3GYKQMLCOIDPCLF4VM6SCP2P6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200810%2F3GYKQMLCOIDPCLF4VM6SCP2P6U%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yuf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=fc6f5d2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200810%2F3GYKQMLCOIDPCLF4VM6SCP2P6U%2F&h=3c0cb6e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200810/3GYKQMLCOIDPCLF4VM6SCP2P6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n部長議員紛請辭 或提前選舉解危機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AYXcu_ukQAsY7lcw2hmNhNZbHCA=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZLVZPXCXES3NGFFP56J6A7YXVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAYXcu_ukQAsY7lcw2hmNhNZbHCA%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZLVZPXCXES3NGFFP56J6A7YXVA.jpg&h=c2bc9b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者一度佔據外交部，宣佈大樓為「革命總部」。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩首都貝魯特發生大爆炸後，不少民眾直指政府管治無能。黎巴嫩的新聞部長薩馬德（Manal Abdel Samad）昨天成為首位於事故後請辭的政府官員，她向民眾道歉指辜負了他們。<br />\n<br />\n「讓民眾選擇誰來管治」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國際援手 當局須承諾展開獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n反對黨、基督教馬龍教派「長槍黨」的三名國會議員前天也請辭，並邀其他議員跟從，「讓民眾選擇誰來管治他們」，令事故後辭職抗議的議員增至五人。<br />\n<br />\n貝魯特大爆炸把社會對執政階級的憤怒推至臨界點，面臨龐大壓力的總理迪亞布前天宣佈，今天會向內閣提出提前國會大選的。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n過去數十年，黎巴嫩內戰後。。。。。。。。。不應由他來為國家的經濟和政治危機負責。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"}]}